comments: Green (GSW) makes marginal contact with Capela (HOU) that does not affect his ability to finish at the rim.
Capela (HOU) places a hand/arm to the front of Curry (GSW) at the start of the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
LAR shows Thompson (GSW) reaches in and makes contact with Gordon's (HOU) wrist, causing him to lose control of the ball.
Looney (GSW) makes incidental contact with Paul's (HOU) off-arm and cleanly blocks his shot attempt at the rim.
Green (GSW) makes contact to the arm of Gordon (HOU) that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Gordon (HOU) and Livingston (GSW) briefly engage with each other while moving in the same direction and then disengage.
Tucker (HOU) makes incidental contact with Curry's (GSW) left hand after he briefly loses control of his dribble on his own.
Looney (GSW) and Tucker (HOU) make incidental contact with each other during the rebound.
Paul (HOU) moves into Curry (GSW) and makes contact to the body that affects his shot attempt.
Curry (GSW) makes marginal contact to the body of Harden (HOU) that does not affect his SQBR.
Tucker (HOU) crowds Thompson (GSW) on the perimeter and makes marginal contact that does not affect his SQBR.
Gordon (HOU) reaches in and initiates contact with Iguodala's (GSW) right arm before he gathers and begins his upward shooting motion.
Capela's (HOU) arm is initially extended when he makes contact with Iguodala (GSW) during the pick, but he collapses his arm and disengages when he moves towards the basket.
Looney (GSW) moves along Harden's (HOU) path to the basket and makes incidental contact that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Paul (HOU) makes marginal contact with Thompson (GSW) that does not dislodge him from his position.

Paul (HOU) and Harden (HOU) trap Thompson (GSW) against the sideline and Thompson jumps backwards to find an opening for the pass.  After reviewing the play from multiple angles and frame-by-frame, there is no conclusive angle that shows the ball touching Thompson's (GSW) fingertips as he lands before releasing the ball on his pass attempt.
Gordon (HOU) dives into Livingston's (GSW) legs and and dislodges him from his position during the loose ball.
Capela (HOU) makes incidental contact to the arm of Thompson (GSW) after the release that does not affect his play at the basket.
Curry (GSW) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Paul (HOU) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
